{"id": 1843, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得哪些产品名称失去了描述产品的能力？", "description": "别整那些有的没的了，先换个辨识度高点的名字吧（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 19341, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170809104107iTk7KdIj0rzgV9sa.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-14T17:00:46Z", "questions": [{"id": 2777, "title": "你觉得哪些产品名称失去了描述产品的能力？", "content": "你觉得哪些产品名称失去了描述产品的能力？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 228198, "content": "不同品牌的产品没啥区分度：电子产品总是P8、S10、V9…", "image": "img/option/option/20170809144956b0oYpI5Fcid2LOHV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228201, "content": "同品牌旗下的子品牌名字太像：汽车爱叫X锐、X腾", "image": "img/option/option/201708091454536oEScTHy2AeLa5b9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228200, "content": "颜色描述乱加形容词：香槟金、魅惑金、活力金、缎面金", "image": "img/option/option/20170809145005I6UjJBbGuizOw0rs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228227, "content": "噱头大于实质，还都用差不多的噱头：护肤品叫奇迹、新生、原液", "image": "img/option/option/20170809165139GMlFnTKp3qgEU2x7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228204, "content": "只顾着文艺和抖机灵：比如掺杂诗词和梗的菜名、餐馆名", "image": "img/option/option/201708091640088eyQqEGlLOYpKV0S.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228203, "content": "过于冗长花哨，比如罗列所有配料：桃花满满焦糖福栗金玉拿铁", "image": "img/option/option/20170809145548S459sYl8trvyCRgI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228229, "content": "直译产品名，很难记：汉尼斯衣帽架、必比斯鞋架……", "image": "img/option/option/20170809164849zm5soTLw6q2fYHrk.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 228240, "content": "过于抽象：从香水名称推断味道，实在是个谜", "image": "img/option/option/20170809165059V2cpuAMfLCsE9mGi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}